adqlQueryList: SELECT object_name AS "Object", object_namespace AS "Namespace", reason AS "Reason", message AS "Message" FROM k8s_event_snapshots WHERE clusterName = "K8s-Cluster-Agent" AND object_name = "app-load-55c75bbd65-8tgmc"
